description: Demolition of Redwood building and buildings in stable yard, and erection of 3 three storey blocks comprising 60 two bedroom and 18 three bedroom flats with 156 car parking spaces in semi-basement, and 39 car parking spaces, single storey extension to Stable Block and conversion into 5 two bedroom terraced houses, two storey block comprising 4 two bedroom and 2 three bedroom flats, 3 two bedroom houses and 2 three bedroom houses with 22 garages and 7 car parking spaces (amendment of scheme permitted under ref. 02/01097 to substitute flat roof design for approved shallow pitched roof on blocks of flats)
